#1  Teen Titans Robin, Wonder Girl, Aqualad and Kid Flash face off against their first opponent in the premiere issue of their very own series: the Beast-God Xochatan! 

#2  When the Teen Titans receive an emergency call from Smedleyville, they discover 16-year-old Penny and her friend Garn--as well as a caveman attacking the people of the city! But what connection do the crazed caveman and Garn share? 

#3  When an usual number of high school students begin dropping out in Harrison, the Teen Titans are called to investigate, sending the team racing against custom cars. 

#4  When a participant in the Olympics goes missing, the Teen Titans go on the search and encounter the secret organization known as Diablo. But the Titans receive some assistance from another teen hero: Speedy! 

#5  Robin asks his teammates for help in uncovering the secret of the Ant, who is terrorizing a reform camp for teenagers run by the friend of the Boy Wonder, Doctor Turner.
